{'title': 'Police Capture CPI (Maoist) Area Commander During Raid In Chatra District', 'publish time': '2023-03-04T05:21:57+00:00', 'update time': '2023-03-04T21:22:27+00:00', 'author': 'Alan Warsaw', 'images': ['https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-cant-remove-handcuffs-once-applied-until-the-restrained-person-is-taken-into-police-custody-800x445.png'], 'text': '![](https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/You-cant-remove-handcuffs-once-applied-until-the-restrained-person-is-taken-into-police-custody-800x445.png)\n\n**Chatra District, March 4, 2023:** An area commander of the CPI (Maoist) wasarrested in Jharkhand’s Chatra district on Saturday, police said.\n\nThe Maoist, identified as Ramashish Yadav alias Chalitar Yadav, was arrestedfrom Kolhua village under Hunterganj police station area, around 170kilometres from the state capital Ranchi.\n\nHe was wanted in around 10 cases at various police stations of the district,Chatra Superintendent of Police Rakesh Ranjan said.\n\nAfter receiving information that Yadav came to the village, a police teamraided it and arrested him, Ranjan said.\n\n> Source : https://theprint.in/india/cpimaoist-area-commander-held-in-> jharkhand/1418592/', 'tags': ['Chalitar Yadav', 'Chatra District', 'CPI (maoist)', 'CPI(maoist)', 'India', 'Jharkhand', 'Naxal', 'naxalites', 'naxals', 'police', 'Political Prisonner', 'PPW in India', 'Ramashish Yadav', 'Ranchi', 'Ranchi District'], 'categories': ['India', "People's War", 'Political Prisoners'], 'source': 'https://www.redspark.nu/en/peoples-war/police-capture-cpi-maoist-area-commander-during-raid-in-chatra-district/'}